diseased brain.
- Shut up, shut up,

01:27:31.773 --> 01:27:33.992
shut up, shut up, shut up!

01:27:36.385 --> 01:27:37.257
- Madelin?

01:27:42.479 --> 01:27:43.349
Madelin?

01:27:47.483 --> 01:27:48.355
Madelin?

01:27:49.747 --> 01:27:51.358
Oh, god, Madelin!

01:27:51.445 --> 01:27:52.924
Fuck, fuck, fuck!

01:27:53.010 --> 01:27:54.883
Madelin, Maddie, Maddie,
Maddie, Maddie.

01:27:54.970 --> 01:27:56.276
Wake up, wake up, wake up.

01:27:57.189 --> 01:27:58.321
Are you alright?

01:27:58.408 --> 01:27:59.714
- What did you do?

01:28:00.584 --> 01:28:02.107
- You wanted me dead.

01:28:02.194 --> 01:28:03.674
- What the fuck?

01:28:03.760 --> 01:28:06.068
- You made me go
into that garage

01:28:06.155 --> 01:28:07.590
so you could take my money.

01:28:07.678 --> 01:28:08.853
- We have to get her
to the hospital.

01:28:08.939 --> 01:28:09.854
